  "remarks": "\nPetrochemical Commercial Company is an involved person under the Iran (Sanctions) Regulations 2023 on the basis of the following ground: Petrochemical Commercial Company \nhas provided support to hostile activity by the Government of Iran, namely activity which is intended to cause the destabilisation of the United Kingdom or any other country.\n",
